text:
Dear Friends

Paccar is coming to campus today. This company does sponsor for some of their roles. This is a company that design and manufacture premium trucks (which must be a plus if you're into country music), located in Bellevue (WA).
There is a chance this is more focused on Supply Chain (as they are also here for the supply chain fair), but it is a big company with many MBA roles.

From 6 to 7pm - Tanner Building Room W240.
